data.Name: JMSN
data.Bio: Christian Berishaj (stage name JMSN) is an American singer, songwriter, multi-instrumentalist, producer, engineer, mixer, videographer and designer. Born in Detroit. Resides in Los Angeles. His debut album is †Priscilla†. (2) Producer/songwriter Christian Berishaj was born in the greater Detroit area and quickly developed a fascination with music and performance. He started recording his own music at age 12 and by the time he was 18 he'd gone through various different bands and projects Read more on Last.fm
